@BlazDT 
My Advanced Protection on iPhone finally works again, but unfortunately the floating banner leftover on the homepage (not subpage as reported) is not handled by any rule with div id `lithium-root`, see Screenshot of this post: https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/172443#issuecomment-1933641877
Can it be filtered, too?
